  "description": "A close-up, slightly overhead shot of a small, spherical cactus covered in long, golden-yellow spines. The cactus is vibrant green at its core, and the spines radiate outwards, creating a textured, almost fuzzy appearance. The cactus sits within a terracotta pot filled with small pebbles and soil.  A blurred green leaf partially frames the top of the image, suggesting a larger plant nearby. The overall composition feels natural and focuses on the intricate details of the cactus.",
